trans-unit.source: Defines identifiers for the standard set of commands that are available to most applications.
trans-unit.target: Define identificadores para o conjunto padrão de comandos que estão disponíveis para a maioria das aplicações.

trans-unit.source: This class defines <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> identifiers for standard commands that are available to designers.
trans-unit.target: Define esta classe <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>identificadores para comandos padrão que estão disponíveis para os estruturadores.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>

trans-unit.source: To add a command from the StandardCommands class to a designer menu, you must call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> method of an <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> and add a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> that contains a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> from StandardCommands.
trans-unit.target: Para adicionar um comando da classe de StandardCommands a um menu estruturador, tem de chamar o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A>método de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>e adicione um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand>que contenha um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>de StandardCommands.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A>

trans-unit.target: Obtém o primeiro de um conjunto de verbos.
Este campo é só de leitura.

trans-unit.source: This is a special <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> that identifies the first of a set of designer verbs.
trans-unit.target: Esta é uma oferta especial de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>que identifica o primeiro de um conjunto de verbos estruturador.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>

trans-unit.source: The Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer automatically maps designer verbs to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A> property on <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, so generally you do not need to access this command.
trans-unit.target: Estruturador do Visual Studio Windows Forms automaticamente mapeia estruturador verbos para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>propriedade <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, geralmente, não precisa de aceder a este comando.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: All designer verbs for an object become commands with a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> within a sequential range of IDs that begins with VerbFirst and ends with <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast>.
trans-unit.target: Todos os verbos estruturador para um objeto ficam comandos com um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>dentro de um sequenciais intervalo de IDs que começa com VerbFirst e termina com <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>
A adicionar.

trans-unit.source: Gets the last of a set of verbs.

Este campo é só de leitura.

trans-unit.source: The Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer automatically maps designer verbs to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A> property on <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, so generally you do not need to access this command.
trans-unit.target: Estruturador do Visual Studio Windows Forms automaticamente mapeia estruturador verbos para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>propriedade <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, geralmente, não precisa de aceder a este comando.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: All designer verbs for an object become commands with a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> within a sequential range of IDs that begins with <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst> and ends with VerbLast.
trans-unit.target: Todos os verbos estruturador para um objeto ficam comandos com um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>dentro de um sequenciais intervalo de IDs que comece com <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst>e termina com VerbLast.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>
